supplies arts at stanford university presented by sica home search this site arts enews subscribe for students supplies in the neighborhood there are two art stores within biking distance of stanford university art off university avenue on hamilton st is well organized well stocked and convenient but slightly more expensive they have every art supply you would need a nice assortment of papers and a custom framing shop you get a 10 discount as a student accent arts is on california avenue it's generally much cheaper than university art but less organized you do however get a 20 discount as a student and the employees are really helpful and fun to talk to check out the discount section for good deals on paints and brushes university art www universityart com 267 hamilton ave parallel to university one block away 650 328 3500 accent arts www accentarts com 392 california ave 650 424 1044 in san francisco if you are in the city and looking to shop for art supplies flax art located at the intersection of market st and valencia st has a huge selection blick art materials and utrecht also offer really great discounts and have online shopping utrecht also has great website to use if you are looking to buy paint sets with reasonably priced paints and often has great discounts on higher quality paints arch is a great supply store for architecture majors but also has standard supplies as well flax art supplies www flaxart com 699 market st 415 552 2355 blick art materials www dickblick com 1414 van ness ave 415 441 6075 utrecht art supply www utrechtart com 149 new montgomery st 415 777 6917 arch www archsupplies com 99 missouri st 415 433 2724 prospective students check out the arts guide your multimedia guide to the arts at stanford stay updated student home events calendar opportunities in review subscribe curricular info majoring minoring creativity course guide arts intensive arts immersion arts circle make it happen money supplies space collaboration promotion beyond sta